    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wihri stahweja preekſch winna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſch tohs eeraudſijis/\ntezzeja teem pretti / no ta Dſih-\nwokta Durwim / un klannijahs\nlihds patt Semmei / un fazziia:\nKUNGS/ ia es jelle Schehlasti-\nbu efmu atraddis tawas Azzis/\ntad ne eij/luhdsains/tawam Kal-\npam fezzen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums taps atneſts kahds\nMasums uhdens/ un masgajeet\nawas Rahjas/ un peefleedsajtees\nappafch fcha Kohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es dabbufchit kahdu\nMaises Kummofu/ ka juhs farwu\nSirđi atspirdsinajat / pehz war-\nat juhs eet/ jo tapehz effat juhs\neejuhsfu Kalpu nahkufchi/ un tee\nzztia: Darri/ ka tu eſſi fazziifs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms tranzahs us\nDſihwokti pee Saras/ un faz-\nja: Steidſees/ nemun tihjato\niltu trihs Niehrus / mihz un\nrri Karraſchas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms notezzeja pee\nhpeem/ un nehme weenu mihk-\nun labbu Teltn/ un deive to\nn Puifcham/ un tas tranzahs\nfataifcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſch nehme Sweestu\nPeenu/ un to Teltn/ ko wiſch\nfataifſiis/ un zehle teem preek-\ná/ un stahweja pats pee teem\npakſch Kohka/ un tee ehde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazziia tee us winnu:\nirr Sara tawa Seewa? un\nſch fazztia: Redſi/ teju Dſih-\nſh.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazziia: Es patee-\nteeſchu pee terwi (zitta Gad-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "dá) ap fcho Laiku; un raugi/\nSarai tawaiSeewai buhs weens\nDehls / un Sara dsirdeja to\nDſihwokta Durwis/ jo tahs bija\nwinneem no pakkatenes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Ahbraäms un Sara\nbija wezzi / un dauds Deenas\npeedsihwojuſchi/ un tas bij mitte-\njees ar Saru buht/ ka Seewahm\nmehds buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad finehjahs Sara pat-\nti pee ſewis / fazzidama: Buhs\ntad man Kahribá dſihwoht/ pehz/\nka es nu wezza efmu / un mans\nKungs wezzigs irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazziia\nus Ahbraänu: Kam irr Sara\nfinehjuſees pahr to / fazzidama:\nwarretu es teefchain dſeindeht\nwezza buhdaina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Buhnu tad jeb kahda Lee-\nta tam KUNGAM ne eespehja-\nma? es ateefchu pee tewi ap fcho\nnoliktu Laiku / tad buhs Sarai\nweens Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sara leedsahs / fazzi-\ndama/ es ne efmu finehjuſees:\nJo ta bihjajahs. Un tas fazziia;\nNe/ tu eſſi finehjuſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tee Wihrt\nno turrenes/ un greesahs uhs So-\ndomu: Un Ahbraäms gabje ar\nteem/ tohs pawaddidams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazziia:\nArrig es preekſch Ahbraäma ap-\nſtehpſchn/ ko es darri?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Ahbraäms buhs par\nweenu leeſu un warrenu Tautu/\nun eekſch winna taps wiſti Lau-\ndis wirs Semmes fivehtiti.\n"
    }
  ],
